  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "Could you please expose `displayName` as an instance variable or method (`this.getDisplayName()`) on the component? Currently, I have to get it via `componentConstructor.displayName` or `originalSpec.displayName` from the component class.\n\nUse case: I’d like to prefix my error messages thrown in a component with its `displayName` and without repeating it (DRY), e.g.\n\n``` javascript\nhandleClick: function (event) {\n  throw new Error(this.displayName + ': Not implemented.');\n}\n```\n\nI found issue #992 but I don’t believe it covers my request.\n",
